    "Frankfurt does allow for multiple species of bullshit (2002: 340).",
    "3 Following this suggestion, we propose to envisage bullshit as a genus, and Frankfurt's intentional bullshit as one species within this genus.",
    "Other species may include that produced by the advertiser, who anticipates that no one will believe their utterances 4 or someone who has no intention one way or another about whether they mislead their audience.",
    "To that end, consider the following distinction:",
    "3 In making this comment, Frankfurt concedes that what Cohen calls \"bullshit\" is also worthy of the name."
